parameters: Karen: "Amasawa... Why can't I stop thinking about him..."

Karen: "Is it just because I'm annoyed with Morisaki, that I want to
take away something precious to her?"
Karen: "Or is it that I'm truly in love with Amasawa?"

Karen: "Even though I've always gotten everything I've wanted..."
Karen: "If only Morisaki wasn't there, if only she wasn't!"
Karen: "No! I can't suppress these feelings..."
